thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Anna Riccio

author: Anna Riccio
title: Anna Riccio
text:
Shannon Tipene is an awesome property manager always focused on Customer Satisfaction. I know she will always do her best to service and support me. She is thorough, quick and detailed. Has the right contacts and always provides advice and knows what's happening in the market.
Pleasure to have her as my property manager
